Welcome to Urban Safari!

Urban-Safari is a roulette events application, where you can find many different events based on date and location.

Choose your favorite events categories. We take care of the rest. This way, we will suggest events you can go to without having to do research.

With our app, you can not just go to an event using the "Feeling Wild" button, but you can host one. Yep, that's right! You can create your event and make it available on the app!

Are you ready to start your adventure? You are a click away from having fun!!

Actions:

- Double click on the map to create your event.
- Click on the "Feeling Wild" button to start your adventure! This button will suggest you an event you may want to go to, based on your preferences.
